{"tid":1701953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益]平日狗隻返工放工如何防止被伏擊？","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T13:02:21.000Z","uid":36525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7e125a126c9681156b3750f6941e1c278fdb04","tid":1701953,"uid":36525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"班呃ot既狗都總有收工一日 收左工自然要返工 又咁多人比人起左底 出哂樣<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地而家點防止比人伏擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你知啦 佢地無左gear同一般人一樣 比人鶳點擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定期出入狗屋既除左揹左保釋既手足之外 有冇狗之外會定期出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有人/機camp住個門口而附近又有無cctv既後卷之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果街坊見到狗沖出黎會唔小心擋到既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣都幾大件事 數下數下就無咁1隻 好易有恐慌出現<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手諗方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee14a3fe55e6b880e6e0314a3bdaffe073caded4","tid":1701953,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-